	&lt;p data-end=&quot;795&quot; data-start=&quot;697&quot;&gt;Provides &lt;strong data-end=&quot;727&quot; data-start=&quot;706&quot;&gt;practical methods&lt;/strong&gt; to &lt;strong data-end=&quot;769&quot; data-start=&quot;731&quot;&gt;assess and reduce carbon emissions&lt;/strong&gt; in the handloom sector.&lt;/p&gt;
