	&lt;li data-end=&quot;1175&quot; data-start=&quot;1090&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;1175&quot; data-start=&quot;1092&quot;&gt;The &lt;strong data-end=&quot;1143&quot; data-start=&quot;1096&quot;&gt;handloom sector employs over 35 lakh people&lt;/strong&gt;, including &lt;strong data-end=&quot;1172&quot; data-start=&quot;1155&quot;&gt;25 lakh women&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
